[normal]BNI0015[bold]&#xa0;[bold]Written evidence submitted by [bold]IBOA [bold]The[bold] Finance Union[bold]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1.[bold]              [bold]Introduction[bold]&#xa0;[bold]1.1
[normal]              
[normal]IBOA The Finance Union represents over 18,000 employees in the financial 
[normal]sector
[normal] in the Republic of Ireland, Northern Ireland and Great Britain – predominantly in banking 
[normal]– 
[normal]of 
[normal]whom
[normal] approximately 5,000 work in Northern Ireland. Members of the Union 
[normal]work in
[normal] many areas within the sector, including 
[normal]some 
[normal]managerial grades.
