[normal]5.[bold]              [bold]The position of the staff of the former Irish Bank Resolution Corporation[bold]&#xa0;[bold]5.1
[normal]              
[normal]The “special liquidation” of the Irish Bank Resolution Corporation (IBRC) by the Irish Parliament earlier this year has created 
[normal]considerable
[normal] difficulty for IBRC’s employees 
[normal]in Northern Ireland and the Republic
[normal] – not least because the consequences for the I
