[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]5.2
[normal]              
[normal] 
[normal]Thi
[normal]s
[normal] legislation 
[normal]may 
[normal]be subject 
[normal]to
[normal] litigation
[normal] – not least because, it has been argued, 
[normal]the 
[normal]company
[normal] was solvent
[normal] at the time
