[normal]5.3
[normal]              
[normal]From the 
[normal]workers’ 
[normal]perspective, th
[normal]e
[normal] liquidation 
[normal]is
[normal] more 
[normal]akin to
[normal] a receivership 
[normal]as
[normal] the company 
[normal]has 
[normal]continue
[normal]d
[normal] to operate as before in wind-down mode but with an accelerated timescale. IBOA has also raised 
[normal]concer
[normal]ns with the EU as to whether the implementation of the 
[normal]Oireachtas
[normal]’ decision has frustrated the European directive on 
[normal]the 
[normal]prote
