[normal]ngs – in the case of IBRC
[normal] 
[normal]staff
[normal] 
[normal]transferring to other entit
[normal]ies – such as Capita 
[normal]and
[normal] NAMA. 
[normal]IBRC
[normal] employees in Northern Ireland
[normal] are further concerned
[normal] that the Irish authorities
[normal] may have
[normal] breached the terms of
[normal] the Revised Credit Facility Agreement governing the bilateral loan of £3.25bn provided by the British Government at the end of 2010.
